	  <concept id="i1073200"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">45.107</ph> Contract clauses.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2611e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2625e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d2611e23" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2625e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Except as provided in paragraph (d) of this section, the contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1047486.dita#i1047486"
                              base="i1047486"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.245-1</xref>, Government Property, in-</p>
							              <ol id="d2611e36" class="- topic/ol ">
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2625e40" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(i)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    All cost-reimbursement and time-and-material type solicitations and contracts, and labor-hour solicitations when property is expected to be furnished for the labor-hour contracts.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2625e49" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(ii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Fixed-price solicitations and contracts when the Government will provide Government property.</p>
								                </li>
								                <li class="- topic/li ">
									                  <p id="d2625e58" class="- topic/p ">
                              <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(iii)</ph>
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
                              
										                    Contracts or modifications awarded under FAR <xref href="FAR-i1113784.dita#i1113784"
                                    base="i1113784"
                                    outputclass="fm:Part"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">partÂ  12</xref> procedures where Government property that exceeds the simplified acquisition threshold, as defined in FAR <xref href="FAR-i1125359.dita#i1125359"
                                    base="i1125359"
                                    outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                                    class="- topic/xref ">2.101</xref>, is furnished or where the contractor is directed to acquire property for use under the contract that is titled in the Government.</p>
								                </li>
							              </ol>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2625e75" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate I in contracts other than those identified in FAR <xref href="FAR-i1073171.dita#i1073171"
                              base="i1073171"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">45.104</xref>(a), Responsibility and Liability for Government Property.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d2625e87" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contracting officer shall use the clause with its Alternate II when a contract for the conduct of basic or applied research at nonprofit institutions of higher education or at nonprofit organizations whose primary purpose is the conduct of scientific research (see <xref href="FAR-i1079632.dita#i1079632"
                              base="i1079632"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">35.014</xref>) is contemplated.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2625e101" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall also insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1047698.dita#i1047698"
                        base="i1047698"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.245-2</xref>, Government Property (Installation Operation Services), in fixed-price service contracts to be performed on a Government installation when Government-furnished property will be provided for initial provisioning only and the Government is not responsible for repair or replacement.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2625e113" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The contracting officer shall insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1047718.dita#i1047718"
                        base="i1047718"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.245-9</xref>, Use and Charges, in solicitations and contracts when the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1047486.dita#i1047486"
                        base="i1047486"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.245-1</xref> is included.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2625e128" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Purchase orders for property repair need not include a Government property clause when the unit acquisition cost of Government property to be repaired does not exceed the simplified acquisition threshold, unless other Government property (not for repair) is provided.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
